CustomField.description: If this is checked, it means that the click that sent a visitor to your web site prior to them submitting a web-to-lead form was on an advertisement (Adwords, Microsoft AdCenter, etc.). Unchecked means they clicked on an organic search result, or the visit was not a search.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If this is checked, it means that the click that sent a visitor to your web site prior to them submitting a web-to-lead form was on an advertisement (Adwords, Microsoft AdCenter, etc.). Unchecked means it was an organic search result or it was not search.
CustomField.label: First Paid Search
